Refine the "Opening PRs or pushing to a remote" CLAUDE.md gate to distinguish branch pushes / PR creation (still gated) from posting PR review threads via the `github-pr-review-pending` / `github-pr-review-submitted` skills (auto-approved per the skill's own invocation contract), so `/pr-review`'s default-on post-back actually fires in fresh sessions instead of being silently swallowed by the gate.
